Package: SuSiEIRLS
Type: Package
Title: SuSiE and MESuSiE for non-Gaussian outcomes via IRLS
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yihe Yang
Maintainer: Yihe Yang <yxy1234@case.edu>
Description: Implements both SuSiE and MESuSiE models for generalized linear models (GLMs) 
    using an Iteratively Reweighted Least Squares (IRLS) algorithm, and for Cox 
    proportional-hazards survival outcomes via score-based sufficient statistics. The 
    package extends the Sum of Single Effects (SuSiE) framework to logistic, negative 
    binomial, and other GLMs, as well as time-to-event data, fine-mapping non-Gaussian 
    and censored outcomes within a unified iterative framework.
